      "text": [
        "4189 - وَ رَوَى مُحَمَّدٌ اَلْحَلَبِيُّ عَنْ أَبِي عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ قَالَ : \"مَنْ لَمْ يُسَمِّ إِذَا ذَبَحَ فَلاَ تَأْكُلْهُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4189 - And Muhammad Al-Halabi narrated from Abu Abdullah (as), who said:\n\"Whoever does not mention the name of Allah (swt) when slaughtering, do not eat (from it).\""
        ]
      }
    }
